1726Sekkhaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā sekkho dhammo uppajjati kammapaccayā…  vipākapaccayā—  vipākaṃ sekkhaṃ ekaṃ khandhaṃ…pe…  āhārapaccayā…  indriyapaccayā…  jhānapaccayā…  maggapaccayā…  sampayuttapaccayā…  vippayuttapaccayā…  atthipaccayā…  natthipaccayā…  vigatapaccayā…  avigatapaccayā.
